{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So, imagine you're standing on a street anywhere in America"},{"time":4000,"text":"and a Japanese man comes up to you and says,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":7000,"text":"\"Excuse me, what is the name of this block?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":9000,"text":"And you say, \"I'm sorry, well, this is Oak Street, that's Elm Street."},{"time":13000,"text":"This is 26th, that's 27th.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":15000,"text":"He says, \"OK, but what is the name of that block?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":17000,"text":"You say, \"Well, blocks don't have names."},{"time":20000,"text":"Streets have names; blocks are just the"},{"time":22000,"text":"unnamed spaces in between streets.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":24000,"text":"He leaves, a little confused and disappointed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"So, now imagine you're standing on a street, anywhere in Japan,"},{"time":31000,"text":"you turn to a person next to you and say,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"\"Excuse me, what is the name of this street?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":35000,"text":"They say, \"Oh, well that's Block 17 and this is Block 16.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"And you say, \"OK, but what is the name of this street?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":42000,"text":"And they say, \"Well, streets don't have names."},{"time":44000,"text":"Blocks have names."},{"time":46000,"text":"Just look at Google Maps here. There's Block 14, 15, 16, 17, 18, 19."},{"time":50000,"text":"All of these blocks have names,"},{"time":52000,"text":"and the streets are just the unnamed spaces in between the blocks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56000,"text":"And you say then, \"OK, then how do you know your home address?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":59000,"text":"He said, \"Well, easy, this is District Eight."},{"time":62000,"text":"There's Block 17, house number one.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"You say, \"OK, but walking around the neighborhood,"},{"time":67000,"text":"I noticed that the house numbers don't go in order.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":69000,"text":"He says, \"Of course they do. They go in the order in which they were built."},{"time":72000,"text":"The first house ever built on a block is house number one."},{"time":75000,"text":"The second house ever built is house number two."},{"time":78000,"text":"Third is house number three. It's easy. It's obvious.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"So, I love that sometimes we need to"},{"time":83000,"text":"go to the opposite side of the world"},{"time":85000,"text":"to realize assumptions we didn't even know we had,"},{"time":87000,"text":"and realize that the opposite of them may also be true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"So, for example, there are doctors in China"},{"time":92000,"text":"who believe that it's their job to keep you healthy."},{"time":95000,"text":"So, any month you are healthy you pay them,"},{"time":97000,"text":"and when you're sick you don't have to pay them because they failed"},{"time":99000,"text":"at their job. They get rich when you're healthy, not sick."},{"time":101000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"In most music, we think of the \"one\""},{"time":106000,"text":"as the downbeat, the beginning of the musical phrase: one, two, three, four."},{"time":110000,"text":"But in West African music, the \"one\""},{"time":112000,"text":"is thought of as the end of the phrase,"},{"time":114000,"text":"like the period at the end of a sentence."},{"time":116000,"text":"So, you can hear it not just in the phrasing, but the way they count off their music:"},{"time":118000,"text":"two, three, four, one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121000,"text":"And this map is also accurate."},{"time":124000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"There's a saying that whatever true thing you can say about India,"},{"time":129000,"text":"the opposite is also true."},{"time":131000,"text":"So, let's never forget, whether at TED, or anywhere else,"},{"time":133000,"text":"that whatever brilliant ideas you have or hear,"},{"time":136000,"text":"that the opposite may also be true."},{"time":138000,"text":"Domo arigato gozaimashita."}]}]}